title: "Unspecified error occurred. Please check the logs for more information."
body: Can't get the latest patch... can i get some help here please

replies.body:
Hey there,

Definitely sounds like something odd is happening, could I get you to send your latest patcher log (Found in the directory below) to **oce-wrenchmen@googlegroups.com** so I can take a look at it.

>C:\Riot Games\League of Legends\Logs\Patcher Logs

Please include a link to your thread in the email.
